{"id": 1815, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x网易新闻】在扑朔迷离的职场生活中，你被你的老板画过哪些饼？", "description": "画饼猛如虎，不知不觉就当了二百五。啊，凶险的职场。（作者：林小妖）", "record_count": 7220, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170817171901GTj1hUqPaYDymvNp.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-18T03:00:54Z", "options": [{"id": 230400, "content": "今天如果8点还在加班就给大家订披萨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 32198}, {"id": 230401, "content": "你是可以做经理的，可我特么只想环游世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108686}, {"id": 230402, "content": "是不是学到了很多？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147851}, {"id": 230658, "content": "等回款下来了，咱们马上就发工资！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052989}, {"id": 230407, "content": "给你各种各样提升自己的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592683}, {"id": 237065, "content": "你可以提出问题，推动产品优化。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868571}, {"id": 230410, "content": "d4", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843320}, {"id": 230412, "content": "老板很看好你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064462}, {"id": 230413, "content": "和老板签股份协议，一万股的清洁股份，然而并没有什么卵用 照样发不起工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062399}, {"id": 230414, "content": "这个项目你们自己研发成功了，给你10%", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712861}, {"id": 230415, "content": "忙完这段时间就轻松了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646307}, {"id": 230418, "content": "应届毕业生，希望你带动部门活跃度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082102}, {"id": 230419, "content": "年底给你加工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875535}, {"id": 230420, "content": "不错，你马上就成功了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108841}, {"id": 230421, "content": "这是一次锻炼的机会。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108845}, {"id": 230423, "content": "进单位后马上参加“巨额”培训费用的培训，你想辞职就要交这批费用回来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990350}, {"id": 230424, "content": "主管做不好要退下来，老板做不好也得退下来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108860}, {"id": 231192, "content": "年底发大奖", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515279}, {"id": 230681, "content": "明年就让你休年假", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914981}, {"id": 230426, "content": "公司还是在用人的时候，机会还是很多的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108874}, {"id": 230427, "content": "加班加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939645}, {"id": 231195, "content": "今天不加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 230429, "content": "给你涨到x你就可以每个月拿到x+y（某个月会发一次的奖金）+z（一年也不一定会有的项目提成）=xx（我给你开了这么高的工资，好好做）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043839}, {"id": 234015, "content": "再坚持几年，你就是下一个鞠婧祎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125507}, {"id": 230434, "content": "年薪百万不是梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870877}, {"id": 230441, "content": "别人老板：我们公司员工工资四千多。某老板：给这么多员工哪有上升动力啊，我就给一千多。某人：呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108964}, {"id": 230443, "content": "公司正在准备上市，今后你将不再是员工，而是合伙人！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108977}, {"id": 230446, "content": "餐饮店，平时老板对卫生很苛刻，只要手碰到食物（不论生或熟）都要带一次性手套，餐具一定要干净消毒，并制定了表格每个月实行扣钱制度来管理店内的卫生。……分界线：然而，店内烤面包的酱和布丁粉都过期了，却因供货商说没关系，一直在用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106380}, {"id": 230450, "content": "送你一套海景房，海要自己挖.", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1109041}, {"id": 230451, "content": "会有年终奖的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243211}, {"id": 230708, "content": "你说的这个薪资不是问题！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015736}, {"id": 230964, "content": "公司很快就要上市了", "image": "img/option/option/20170822192614lc93RGbIJudUOzvD", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111439}, {"id": 230456, "content": "这是最后一版，干完下班", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880861}, {"id": 230712, "content": "这个项目完成,我分给你股份", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110486}, {"id": 230467, "content": "这是一个学习的机会，好好把握", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050667}, {"id": 230468, "content": "忙过这阵就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050667}, {"id": 230469, "content": "等忙完这个段时间，给你放个长假，让你好好休息休息～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009879}, {"id": 224839, "content": "去大连出差说要请吃海鲜，当晚唯一海产品是裙带菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 174, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 230471, "content": "我们来谈谈理想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 232263, "content": "我老板从不画饼，答应的都能做到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115878}, {"id": 234055, "content": "我们自己开公司自己说了算,睡到太阳晒屁股,不打卡上班.忙个一两年把公司卖一个亿,大家各自分钱散伙.该买房的买房,该旅游的旅游.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984202}, {"id": 236103, "content": "再也不是250", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133878}, {"id": 224840, "content": "创业公司许我期权，试用期还没过公司就倒闭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 253, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 230472, "content": "年轻人要有理想，现在少挣点没关系，我保证………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 224841, "content": "“马上到财年要调薪了，我很看好你。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 230217, "content": "你还要不要你的政治前途了", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107937}, {"id": 224842, "content": "“再熬几个大夜，这个项目完了年底奖金就有着落了。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 365, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 230218, "content": "员工股权", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092884}, {"id": 230474, "content": "我见过太多人拔苗助长的，你还是要慢慢来，最好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050348}, {"id": 230219, "content": "多学多干年终奖翻倍\r\n公司马上就要上市敲钟了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961285}]}